{"tid":2296821,"cid":21,"subCid":3,"title":"日本2000-2009年音樂討論 jpop","createTime":"2020-11-22T21:15:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T03:57:04.000Z","uid":353647,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6f4a90322e6d9bc3c6ba6ef3c277fa2fc729ed19","tid":2296821,"uid":353647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T21:15:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gIiC1ySxe8M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgIiC1ySxe8M&d=icC9UeWzMg70WCHWfTItT4leFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=1cceb709\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gIiC1ySxe8M</a><br />\n以上為日本 Oricon single ranking 100強<br />\n首首好經典<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，好百花齊放。唔似2009年打後，已經係數字團天下。呢個時候偶像派同其他派系都勢勻力敵。<br />\n而我係2008年，屋企買第一部高清電視，睇music station而鍾意咗日文歌，個個星期都追。<br />\n<br />\n依加都十幾年了，今日打開music station個網頁，鍾意嘅歌手，已經冇邊隊見到佢上，啲嘉賓都好陌生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。打開oricon榜，由上至下望咗幾秒，默默點擊上一頁...可能我一直依戀緊十幾年前嘅時光<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40c7409086576082ec1b16f65cc65e3eccd2adef","tid":2296821,"uid":69985,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T21:44:51.000Z","msg":"jpop 既黃金時代<br />\n好多歌都好好聽又經典"},{"pid":"1cb01a7068f441023e02b636eb2b72eab5aabf3f","tid":2296821,"uid":236359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T01:37:21.000Z","msg":"到00年代啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c063afe221b49ad8f6df0b9f772b96496f42f9ed","tid":2296821,"uid":71085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T01:50:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3b4330c2fa83f166f519b339101725c93a7e853b","tid":2296821,"uid":353647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c063afe221b49ad8f6df0b9f772b96496f42f9ed","tid":2296821,"uid":71085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T01:50:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T01:53:1